<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Bayesian phylogram inferred from 28 S (region D 2 - D 3) sequence data aligned by secondary structure. Bayesian analysis runtime = 736,000 generations (25 % burnin). Branch support: Bayesian posterior probabilities / bootstrap (1,000 replicates). (-) indicates bootstrap support below 60." , "Figure 28. Camptothlipsis sheilae sp. n. a anterior head b lateral head and mesosoma c dorsal head and mesothorax d dorsal propodeum and metasomal terga 1 and 2. Arrows show positions for length and width measurements e fore wing." , "Figure 27. Camptothlipsis sheilae sp. n. a lateral habitus b dorsal habitus." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11199" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11248" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/11247" .

